quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  21,58,"fhtm 'iibrahim al'asnam wajaealaha qteana sghyrt, wtrk kbyrha; kay yarjie alqawm 'iilayh wysalwh, fytbyn ejzhm wdlalhm, wataqum alhujat elyhm"
  21,59,"wrje alqwm, wara'awua asnamhm mhtmt mhant, fsal bedhm bedana: man faeal hdha balhtna? 'iinah lzalm fi ajtrayh ealaa alalihat almustahaqat lltezym waltwqyr"
  21,60,"qal man sumie 'iibrahim yhlf bi'anah sykyd asnamhm: samiena fatana yuqal lah 'ibrahym, yadhkur al'asnam bsw'"
  21,61,"qal rwsawhm: fatu bi'iibrahim ealaa mar'aa min alnas; kay yshhdu ealaa aetrafh bima qal; liakun dhlk hujat elyh"
  21,62,"wjy' bi'iibrahim wsalwh mnkryn: 'a'ant aldhy kssart alhtna? yenwn asnamhm"
  21,63,"wtmm li'iibrahim ma 'arad min 'iizhar sfhhm ealaa mar'aa mnhm. faqal mhtjana ealayhim merridana bghbawthm: bal aldhy kssarha hdha alsnm alkbyr, fas'aluu alihatakum almzewmt ean dhlk, 'iin kanat tatakalam 'aw tuhyr jwabana"
  21,64,"f'usqit fi aydyhm, wabada lahum dlalhm; kayf yebdwnha, wahi eajizat ean 'an tadfae ean nafsiha shyyana 'aw 'an tjyb saylha? waqrru ealaa 'anfusahum balzlm walshrk"
  21,65,"wsurean ma ead 'iilayhim enadhm baed 'ifhamhm, fanqalabuu 'iilaa albatl, wahtjju ealaa 'iibrahim bima hu hujat lah elyhm, fqalu: kayf nsalha, waqad elmt 'anaha la tntq?"
  21,66,"qal 'iibrahim mhqqirana lshan alasnam: kayf taebudun asnamana laa tanfae 'iidha eubdt, wala tdrr 'iidha turkt? qbhana lakum wlalhtkm alty tebdwnha min dun allah teala، 'afala taeqilun ftdrkwn su' ma 'antum elyh?"
  21,67,"qal 'iibrahim mhqqirana lshan alasnam: kayf taebudun asnamana laa tanfae 'iidha eubdt, wala tdrr 'iidha turkt? qbhana lakum wlalhtkm alty tebdwnha min dun allah teala، 'afala taeqilun ftdrkwn su' ma 'antum elyh?"
  21,68,"lma btlt hujatuhum wazahar alhaqu eadaluu 'iilaa aistiemal sltanhm, wqalu: harriqu 'iibrahim balnar; ghdbana lalhtkm 'iin kuntum naasirin lha. fashealu narana ezymt wa'alquh fyha, fantasir allah larasuluh waqal llnar: kuni brdana wslamana ealaa 'ibrahym, falam yanalh fiha adha, walam ysbh mkrwh"
  21,69,"lma btlt hujatuhum wazahar alhaqu eadaluu 'iilaa aistiemal sltanhm, wqalu: harriqu 'iibrahim balnar; ghdbana lalhtkm 'iin kuntum naasirin lha. fashealu narana ezymt wa'alquh fyha, fantasir allah larasuluh waqal llnar: kuni brdana wslamana ealaa 'ibrahym, falam yanalh fiha adha, walam ysbh mkrwh"
  21,70,"warad alqawm bi'iibrahim alhlak fabtl allah kydhm, wjelhm almghlwbyn alasflyn"
  21,71,"wnjyna 'iibrahim wlwtana aladhi aman bih min \"aleraq\", wakhrjnahma 'iilaa 'ard \"alsham\" alati barakna fiha bikathrat alkhyrat, wafiha 'akthar al'anbia' ealayhim alsalat walslam"
  21,72,"wanem allah ealaa 'ibrahym, fawahab lah aibnih 'iishaq hin deah, wwhb lah min 'iishaq yaequb ziadat ealaa dhlk, wkll min 'iibrahim wa'iishaq wayaequb jaealah allah salhana mtyeana lh"